com.siperian.sif.message.mrm

Class PutDependentObjectResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.siperian.sif.message.SiperianResponse
      • com.siperian.sif.message.mrm.PutResponse
        • com.siperian.sif.message.mrm.PutDependentObjectResponse
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RecordKeyProvider, Serializable
    Deprecated. 
    As of 9.0

    public class PutDependentObjectResponse
extends PutResponse
    This class is the response to a PutDependentObjectRequest. The contents of the response are identical to that of a PutResponse with one additional field. GetDependentSourceKey will contain the source key of the dependent object that was inserted or updated.

    See PutDependentObjectRequest

    See Also:
    Record, PutResponse, PutRequest, PutDependentObjectRequest, Serialized Form

    API Pair: PutDependentObjectRequest

    API Group: Data Update/Insert
